➜山西襄汾县一饭店坍塌多人被困，事发时一老人正在过寿
http://www.sohu.com/a/415518923_114988	32948
<div id="sohuplayer">
<script type="text/javascript" src="//tv.sohu.com/upload/swf/showVrsPlayer.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
showVrsPlayer({
